each team is wearing a different-coloured top to their teammates.\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 650, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"keen-eyed spectators\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"each team\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"a different-coloured top\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"their teammates\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The player in question, known as a libero, is a defensive specialist, and their jersey contrasts the rest of the team's outfit, but is usually still in one of the nation's official colours.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The player\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"question\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"a libero\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"a defensive specialist\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"their jersey\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"the team's outfit\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's official colours\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A volleyball squad has 12 members, and two of them can be assigned as 'libero', a position that comes with restrictions.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A volleyball squad\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"12 members\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"libero\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"restrictions\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are only allowed in the back row, and cannot block an attack at the net or jump and spike a ball in the front row.\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the back row\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"an attack\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"the net\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"a ball\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"the front row\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The position was introduced by the International Volleyball Federation in 1996, and the organisation is in charge of the sport at the Games.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1120, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9d\\u00e9ration_Internationale_de_Volleyball\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Volleyball Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9d\\u00e9ration_Internationale_de_Volleyball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9d\\u00e9ration_Internationale_de_Volleyball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The position\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisation\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The different coloured top is to aid referees to be able to see them easily and enforce the restrictions of the position.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The different coloured top\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"referees\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"the restrictions\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"the position\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Volleyball has been in theOlympicssince the debut at Tokyo 1964, and matches are the best of five sets.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1964_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999996134648, \"rank\": 3.8649991263680123e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo 1964\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1964_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1964_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Volleyball\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicssince\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"the debut\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"five sets\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first four sets are played until one reaches 25 points, and if the teams are tied after four sets, the final set is played for, but only until a team scores 15 points.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first four sets\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"25 points\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"the teams\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"four sets\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"the final set\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"15 points\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The libero is one of the positions in the sport, which also has a setter, middle blocker, outside hitter and weakside hitter.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The libero\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"the positions\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"a setter\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1699}, {\"ngram\": \"middle blocker\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"outside hitter\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"weakside hitter\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although the squads can have 12 players, only six are allowed on the court at any one time, and they are separated by a net in the middle.\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the squads\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"12 players\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"any one time\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1844}, {\"ngram\": \"a net\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Teams can have three consecutive touches before they have to hit the ball into the opposing side of the net.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Teams\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"three consecutive touches\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"the opposing side\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"the net\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2055, \"end\": 2066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999364311510422, \"rank\": 4.010360394627142e-05, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"their replies\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"inPlease\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"your brows